        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer126974370" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11637946655352268267">I loved Judy Blume as a kid. I had no idea that she wrote books for adults until my last library visit. When I happened about this book, I was anxious to enjoy some more of the author I had loved as a little girl. <br/><br/>However, her books for adults leave a lot to be desired. This book was basically about a lot of really selfish people having a lot of really random sex and ruining a lot of people&apos;s lives. I wasn&apos;t a fan.</span>
  <span id="freeText11637946655352268267" style="display:none">I loved Judy Blume as a kid. I had no idea that she wrote books for adults until my last library visit. When I happened about this book, I was anxious to enjoy some more of the author I had loved as a little girl. <br /><br />However, her books for adults leave a lot to be desired. This book was basically about a lot of really selfish people having a lot of really random sex and ruining a lot of people's lives. I wasn't a fan.</span>
